item.title: 【Albums (lossy)】MP3 - Silent Hill: Otherworld Echoes (Vol. 2) [2023]
item.description:
Silent Hill: Otherworld Echoes (Vol. 2) is the second compilation of covers of the Silent Hill soundtracks, originally performed by Akira Yamaoka, Daniel Licht, Mary Elizabeth McGlynn and Joe Romersa. These songs were masterfully covered by talented singers and rock bands who honored the video game franchise with their music. Thank you so much, the credit is all yours. You deserved so much recognition for this and hell of subscribers. That's why I'm inviting you to subscribe to their YouTube channels and other platforms so that you can enjoy their amazing musical performances. Special thanks to @ChrisMusick and @danysimardofficial for their talented voices and magical interpretations. The playlist cover was designed by https://vk.com/dan.mason.

Tracklist:

1. Theme of Laura - GaMetal
2. Love Psalm - Chris Musick
3. Acceptance - Alisa Nesterowskaja
4. Letter From The Lost Days - Chjolo & Michael Garrett Steele
5. Hell Frozen Rain - Filip Čačić Feat. Vedrana Šurina
6. Hometown - Dany Simard
7. Tender Sugar - Zmicier Yarmola Feat. Lilith Wine
8. Hole In The Sky - Chris Musick
9. When You're Gone - Claude D.
10. Elle Theme - Jadranka "Tzeetzah" Stanić
11. Now We're Free - Marty Eli Bower
12. Blow Back - Giselle Korsakov
13. This Sacred Line - Chris Musick

Bonus Tracks:

14. Acceptance (Rock Version) - Dany Simard
15. I Want Love (Game Version) - Edgar Rothermich Feat. Romina Arena
